        "description": "Summarize web page content from any URL. Uses WebScrapingService to extract content, then AI Manager to generate summary.\n\n**Flow:** URL → WebScrapingService → AI Manager → Summary\n\n**Note:** This endpoint is async but uses the same endpoint pattern.\n\n**Response:** Returns job_id for polling status and result."
      },
      "response": []
