    {
      "name": "7. Get Available Models",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{bearer_token}}",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/models",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "models"]
        },
        "description": "Get list of available AI models for summarization.\n\n**Response includes:**\n- available_models: Array of model objects with key, vendor, display\n- count: Number of available models\n\n**Common models:**\n- deepseek-chat (default)\n- ollama:llama3\n- ollama:mistral\n- gpt-4o\n- gpt-3.5-turbo"
